ygData.messageBody:
If you have a Selos Drum, this song adds a very nice chunk of AC - like 34
iirc.

Any druids, wizards, clerics, ragners, heck anyone not interested in a free
dose of 34 AC?

I liked it alot - I was using the 3 chants (percussion) so it was quite nice
to fire this song up - at least for the incoming pull and give everyone +34
AC without swapping weps or instruments.

"What is this 'you feel small...' message?"

"+34 AC - look at your stats"

Sylly

Is there only one lvl 52 song?
